snippet.title: Knights of Honor II: Sovereign | Showcase Trailer 2022
snippet.description:
Become the Sovereign and fight for control of Europe in this fresh take on medieval grand strategy: Knights of Honor II: Sovereign. 

Choose your royal court carefully and determine the destiny of your people, be it riches, conquest, intrigue, trade, or defeat! Raise armies to defend your lands or bring the war to your enemy's doorstep - even jump directly into battle in action-packed RTS combat. 

Knights of Honor II: Sovereign is coming to PC.
 
- Links & Info - 
Steam: https://thqn.net/koh2-steam 
Discord: https://discord.gg/knightsofhonor
